	from other warnings.  Add -Wc++-compat to C-specific warnings.
	Check for --enable-build-with-cxx.  Set and substitute
	ENABLE_BUILD_WITH_CXX.  Invoke ZW_PROG_COMPILER_DEPENDENCIES
